{"title_page": "Romeo (2014 film)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2015}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name = Romeo\n| image = Romeo Poster HD.jpg\n| writer = [[Puri Jagannadh]]\n| starring = [[Sairam Shankar]]<br>Adonika\n| director = Gopi Ganesh\n| cinematography =  [[P.G. Vinda]]\n| producer = Dorai Swamy\n| editing = Navin Nooli\n| fights = \n| distributor = \n| country = India\n| released = {{Film date|df=yes|2014|10|10}}\n| runtime =\n| language = Telugu\n| music = [[Sunil Kashyap]]\n| awards =\n| budget = \n| gross = \n}}\n\n'''''Romeo''''' (Telugu: \u0c30\u0c4b\u0c2e\u0c3f\u0c2f\u0c4b) is a 2014 Telugu drama film starring [[Sairam Shankar]] and Adonika in the Lead directed by Gopi Ganesh. Valluripalli Ramesh Produced this Movie on Maharshi Cinema Banner and Sunil Kashyap provided the Music for the film.\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Sairam Shankar]] as Kittu \n* Adonika as Madhoo \n* [[Subbaraju]]\n* [[Pragathi (actress)|Pragathi]]\n* [[Ravi Teja]] in a cameo\n\n\n==Production==\nPuri rasina prema katha is the tag line of this film and [[Puri Jagannadh]] has written the dialogues, which is the first time that the director has written for a film not directed by him. The film is set in Verona, where Shakespeare's drama too was set. This is the only similarity between that Romeo and this modern day 'Romeo', the makers said.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/sairam-shankars-romeo-to-release-soon/263798-71-216.html|title=Sairam Shankar's 'Romeo' to release soon|publisher=IBN Live|accessdate=2 June 2012 <!-- at 10:47am IST --> }}</ref> It was reported that the actor has silently completed the shooting of the film and major portions of the film have been reportedly shot in Europe and at present, only two songs are now left for the film to be completed.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://apnaindia.com/entertainment/gossip/telugu/sairam-shankar-is-romeo-8673.html|title=Sairam Shankar is Romeo|publisher=apnaindia.com|accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External Links==\n{{IMDb title|tt4112274}}\n\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2010s Telugu-language films]]\n[[Category:2014 films]]\n\n\n{{2010s-Telugu-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2015}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name = Romeo\n| image = Romeo Poster HD.jpg\n| writer = [[Puri Jagannadh]]\n| starring = [[Sairam Shankar]]<br>Adonika\n| director = Gopi Ganesh\n| cinematography =  [[P.G. Vinda]]\n| producer = Dorai Swamy\n| editing = Navin Nooli\n| fights = \n| distributor = \n| country = India\n| released = {{Film date|df=yes|2014|10|10}}\n| runtime =\n| language = Telugu\n| music = [[Sunil Kashyap]]\n| awards =\n| budget = \n| gross = \n}}\n\n'''''Romeo''''' (Telugu: \u0c30\u0c4b\u0c2e\u0c3f\u0c2f\u0c4b) is a 2014 Telugu drama film starring [[Sairam Shankar]] and Adonika in the Lead directed by Gopi Ganesh. Valluripalli Ramesh Produced this Movie on Maharshi Cinema Banner and Sunil Kashyap provided the Music for the film.\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Sairam Shankar]] as Kittu \n* Adonika as Madhoo \n* [[Subbaraju]]\n* [[Pragathi (actress)|Pragathi]]\n* [[Ravi Teja]] in a cameo\n\n\n==Production==\nPuri rasina prema katha is the tag line of this film and [[Puri Jagannadh]] has written the dialogues, which is the first time that the director has written for a film not directed by him. The film is set in Verona, where Shakespeare's drama too was set. This is the only similarity between that Romeo and this modern day 'Romeo', the makers said.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/sairam-shankars-romeo-to-release-soon/263798-71-216.html|title=Sairam Shankar's 'Romeo' to release soon|publisher=IBN Live|accessdate=2 June 2012 <!-- at 10:47am IST --> }}</ref> It was reported that the actor has silently completed the shooting of the film and major portions of the film have been reportedly shot in Europe and at present, only two songs are now left for the film to be completed.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://apnaindia.com/entertainment/gossip/telugu/sairam-shankar-is-romeo-8673.html|title=Sairam Shankar is Romeo|publisher=apnaindia.com|accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2010s Telugu-language films]]\n[[Category:2014 films]]\n\n\n{{2010s-Telugu-film-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Vikki5456", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eExternal Links)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romeo_(2014_film)"}
{"title_page": "Who Is the First Wife of My Father", "text_new": "{{EngvarB|date=July 2017}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}}\n\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = who is the first wife of my father\n| image          = Who is the first wife of my father.jpg\n| director       = [[Zeeshan Ahmad]]\n| producer       = [[Dhiraj Rokad]]<br />[[Amit Rokad]]<br />Shiva Sharma\n| story          = Zeeshan Ahmad\n| music          = Gaurav H Singh\n| starring       = [[Inder Kumar]]<br />[[Aditi Govitrikar]]<br />[[Mohan Kapoor]]<br />[[Vaishnavi Mahant]]\n| country        = India\n| runtime        = 119 minutes\n| language       = Hindi\n}}\n\n'''Who is the first wife of my father'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jagran.com/entertainment/bollywood-who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-release-soon-14708704.html|title=Who is the first wife of my father will release soon|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> is an upcoming Indian Hindi movie based on family drama. This movie is directed by Zeeshan Ahmad and produced by Dhiraj Rokad, Amit Rokad and Shiva Sharma. Cast of this movie are Inder Kumar,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dewmedia.in/2016/09/17/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-soon-release/|title='\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926\u093f \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0911\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930' \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c - Dew Media|date=2016-09-17|website=Latest News in Hindi|language=hi|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> Aditi Govitrikar, Mohan Kapoor and Vaishnavi Mahant. Ep of this movie is Vishal Manani. The film<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.arrechintu.com/latest-news/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-is-a-different-type-of-an-art-film/|title=\u0905\u0932\u0917 \u0924\u0930\u0939 \u0915\u0940 \u0906\u0930\u094d\u091f \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 '\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926 \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0906\u0945\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930'|date=2016-09-01|language=en-US|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> is scheduled to be released in 2018.\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Inder Kumar]]\n* [[Aditi Gowitrikar]]\n* [[Vaishnavi Mahant]]\n* [[Mohan Kapoor]]\n* [[Geet Sharma]]\n* [[Nandini Shrivastav]]\n\n==Soundtrack==\n{| border=\"4\" cellpadding=\"7\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" align=\"center\"\n! # !! Title !! Singer(s)\n|-\n| 1\n| Tum Kahan Kho Gaye\n| [[Palak Muchhal]]\nMusic Gaurav H Singh\n|-\n| 2\n| Eso Jiya Main\n| [[Divya Kumar (singer)]]\n|-\n| 3\n| Mere Khuda\n| [[Mohammed Irfan (singer)]]\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n<ref>http://www.zoomtv.com/bollywood-news/article/bollywood-actor-inder-kumar-passes-away-at-the-age-of-45-due-to-a-cardiac-arrest/39398</ref>\n<ref name=\"arrechintu\">{{cite web|url=https://www.arrechintu.com/latest-news/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-is-a-different-type-of-an-art-film/|publisher=arrechintu.com|title=&#039;Who Is The First Wife Of My Father&#039; Is A Different type of An Art film|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"filmysansaar\">{{cite web|url=http://filmysansaar.com/blog/first-wife-father-way-rock-screens/|publisher=filmysansaar.com|title=Filmy Sansaar WHO IS THE FIRST WIFE OF MY FATHER IS ON ITS WAY TO ROCK SCREENS &#124; Filmy Sansaar|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"indiaaajkalnews\">{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaaajkalnews.com/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-release-soon/|publisher=indiaaajkalnews.com|title=\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926\u093f \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0911\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930 \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c - India Aaj Kal|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"jagran\">{{cite web|url=ht