my father'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jagran.com/entertainment/bollywood-who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-release-soon-14708704.html|title=Who is the first wife of my father will release soon|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> is an upcoming Indian Hindi movie based on family drama. This movie is directed by Zeeshan Ahmad and produced by Dhiraj Rokad, Amit Rokad and Shiva Sharma. Cast of this movie are Inder Kumar,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dewmedia.in/2016/09/17/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-soon-release/|title='\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926\u093f \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0911\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930' \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c - Dew Media|date=2016-09-17|website=Latest News in Hindi|language=hi|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> Aditi Govitrikar, Mohan Kapoor and Vaishnavi Mahant. Ep of this movie is Vishal Manani. The film<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.arrechintu.com/latest-news/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-is-a-different-type-of-an-art-film/|title=\u0905\u0932\u0917 \u0924\u0930\u0939 \u0915\u0940 \u0906\u0930\u094d\u091f \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 '\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926 \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0906\u0945\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930'|date=2016-09-01|language=en-US|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref> is scheduled to be released in 2018.\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Inder Kumar]]\n* [[Aditi Gowitrikar]]\n* [[Vaishnavi Mahant]]\n* [[Mohan Kapoor]]\n* [[Geet Sharma]]\n* [[Nandini Shrivastav]]\n\n==Soundtrack==\n{| border=\"4\" cellpadding=\"7\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" align=\"center\"\n! # !! Title !! Singer(s)\n|-\n| 1\n| Tum Kahan Kho Gaye\n| [[Palak Muchhal]]\nMusic Gaurav H Singh\n|-\n| 2\n| Eso Jiya Main\n| [[Divya Kumar (singer)]]\n|-\n| 3\n| Mere Khuda\n| [[Mohammed Irfan (singer)]]\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n<ref>http://www.zoomtv.com/bollywood-news/article/bollywood-actor-inder-kumar-passes-away-at-the-age-of-45-due-to-a-cardiac-arrest/39398</ref>\n<ref name=\"arrechintu\">{{cite web|url=https://www.arrechintu.com/latest-news/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-is-a-different-type-of-an-art-film/|publisher=arrechintu.com|title=&#039;Who Is The First Wife Of My Father&#039; Is A Different type of An Art film|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"filmysansaar\">{{cite web|url=http://filmysansaar.com/blog/first-wife-father-way-rock-screens/|publisher=filmysansaar.com|title=Filmy Sansaar WHO IS THE FIRST WIFE OF MY FATHER IS ON ITS WAY TO ROCK SCREENS &#124; Filmy Sansaar|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"indiaaajkalnews\">{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaaajkalnews.com/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-release-soon/|publisher=indiaaajkalnews.com|title=\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926\u093f \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0911\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930 \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c - India Aaj Kal|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"jagran\">{{cite web|url=http://www.jagran.com/entertainment/bollywood-who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-release-soon-14708704.html|publisher=jagran.com|title=Who is the first wife of my father will release soon 14708704|accessdate=2016-09-26}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"dewmedia\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dewmedia.in/2016/09/17/who-is-the-first-wife-of-my-father-will-soon-release/|publisher=dewmedia.in|title=&#039;\u0939\u0942 \u0907\u091c \u0926\u093f \u092b\u0930\u094d\u0938\u094d\u091f \u0935\u093e\u0907\u092b \u0911\u092b \u092e\u093e\u0908 \u092b\u093e\u0926\u0930&#039; \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c - Dew Media|accessdate=2016-09-26}